    "description": "<p>We are a Chartered Accounting Firm established since 1973 and have a very good client base.</p>\n<p>Our clients are from a wide range of industries, from manufacturers, diamond and jewelry wholesalers, shipping, merchants, investment holding companies, biotech companies, oil and bio fuel, coffee bean suppliers, chains of restaurants and cafes, finance companies and fund managers, IT hardware and software, construction and engineering, paper processing companies etc. both local and international. We also provide financial due diligence services in addition to audits.</p>",
